OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister faces stiff
OL,4,Copposition to proposed income tax rise
OL,6,FDeputy Trott said: "Politics is a
OL,7,Fjourney and we've all been on that
OL,8,Fjourney and as the fiscal position has
OL,9,Fdeteriorated, the arguments have been
OL,10,Fmore accurately articulated around
OL,11,Fwhat we don't get if we starve our
OL,12,Feconomy of investment.
OL,14,F"I think more and more people have
OL,15,Frealised that this just can't go on
OL,16,Fand one of the most striking
OL,17,Fstatistics is the fact that we spend
OL,18,F14% less on a per capita basis on
OL,19,Fpublic services here in Guernsey than
OL,20,Four nearest neighbour and closest
OL,21,Ffriends in Jersey.
