OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister faces stiff
OL,4,Copposition to proposed income tax rise
OL,6,F"These are stark statistics that are
OL,7,Faccurate and can't be ignored."
OL,9,FDeputy Trott's Budget currently faces
OL,10,F22 amendments put forward by States
OL,11,Fmembers.
OL,13,FThe first amendment to be discussed
OL,14,Fwas one from Deputy Charles Parkinson,
OL,15,Fwho wants to see changes to Guernsey's
OL,16,Fcorporate tax system.
