OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister faces stiff
OL,4,Copposition to proposed income tax rise
OL,6,FDeputy Parkinson said: "We have loaded
OL,7,Fso much tax onto the shoulders of the
OL,8,Fmiddle classes in Guernsey that people
OL,9,Fare really struggling and it's not
OL,10,Ffair because some companies are paying
OL,11,Fnothing.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, some very rich
OL,14,Findividuals are using companies to
OL,15,Fshelter their income and they're
OL,16,Fpaying nothing as well, so that just
OL,17,Fincreases the burden further on the
OL,18,Fordinary people of Guernsey - it's
OL,19,Fjust not fair."
